-call-of-the-tempestarii-prime-vault-hotfix-3008-30081/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Zephyr Prime, Chroma Prime, Tiberon Prime, Kronen Prime, Rubico Prime, and Gram Prime Relics have been added to the drop tables! These Relics have replaced the Banshee and Mirage Relics in the drop tables, Bounties, and Relic Packs.\nKronen Prime\nKronen Prime"},{"name":"Saint of Altra: Update 25.7.0","date":"2019-08-29T21:35:56Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1123841-saint-of-altra-update-2570/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed holster issues with the Kronen Prime on numerous Warframes. "},{"name":"Chimera: Update 23.10","date":"2018-10-12T13:56:43Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1016610-chimera-update-2310/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed issues with the Kronen Prime not behaving nicely in the Foundry and Arsenal. "},{"name":"The Sacrifice: Hotfix 23.0.3 - Limbo Prime","date":"2018-06-19T17:58:18Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/971211-the-sacrifice-hotfix-2303-limbo-prime/","additions":"","changes":"Limbo Prime, Destreza Prime, and Pyrana Prime Relics have replaced all locations of Zephyr Prime, Tiberon Prime, and Kronen Prime Relics:\n*Zephyr Prime, Tiberon Prime, and Kronen Prime Relics are also still out in the wild, just not in exclusive spots like Bounties or Onslaught.","fixes":""},{"name":"Shrine of the Eidolon: Hotfix 22.16.5 + 22.16.5.1","date":"2018-03-21T21:38:31Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/936239-shrine-of-the-eidolon-hotfix-22165-221651/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Zephyr Prime, Tiberon Prime, and Kronen Prime (and their respective Relics) not having Codex entries. This resulted in the inability to Chat Link the items and their Relics if you did not own them."}],"wikiAvailable":true,"attacks":[{"name":"Normal Attack","speed":1.17,"crit_chance":22,"crit_mult":2,"status_chance":34,"damage":{"impact":21.2,"slash":169.6,"puncture":21.2},"slide":"424"},{"name":"Slam Attack","spee